OnShareTransfer_Integration_Concrete_Test
├── when caller not vault share token
│  └── it should revert
└── when caller vault share token
   ├── given no adapter
   │  └── it should do nothing
   └── given adapter
      ├── given sender balance zero
      │  └── it should revert
      └── given sender balance not zero
         ├── it should decrease the sender wstETH balance in adapter
         ├── it should increase the recipient wstETH balance in adapter
         └── it should emit a {TransferStakedTokens} event
